creator: Higher Learning Technologies Inc
descriptionHtml:
Want to extend your ASE certifications? The easiest path to success is here!

With the ASE Renewal App, you can earn official credits on-the-go to extend your ASE certification, without going to a testing center or taking away valuable time and money.

How does it work?
Correct questions = credits. Earn credits for every question you answer correct.

Answer questions to get credits. Each month, you’ll receive a new question to answer. Now, you can complete the questions at your own pace.

Did you answer incorrectly? Not a problem — try again! There are more than enough opportunities to earn required credits. So, when you miss a question, that’s okay! Future questions will help you grasp concepts.

Meet your required credit tally and celebrate your recertification. Keep track of your progress towards your recertification with detailed statistics

Created in partnership with the Automotive Service Excellence (ASE), the ASE Renewal App is a vital resource in your career as a technician.

Questions? Feedback? Email us at professional@hltcorp.com
